{"tid":1126071,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"瓦萊黑鼻羊好得意啊！不動的時候還以為牠們只是毛公仔玩具！","createTime":"2019-04-26T06:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T08:35:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab3b88ef2cbe133e82ff21c684332464518ec8a","tid":1126071,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:21:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pAZm19Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpAZm19Z.png&h=2e1e5e7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好萌好得意啊！<br />\n<br />\n瓦萊黑鼻羊原產瑞士瓦萊州，是一種能夠適應高山及嚴寒氣候嘅羊隻品種。全身只得臉部及四肢為黑色。不動的時候還以為牠們只是毛公仔玩具！還有牠們是有眼能看東西的！在英國、紐西蘭及蘇格蘭都能找到牠們蹤影，好搞笑呀！"},{"pid":"af8c3d721e5e5615e76177c072f4abd2cee79088","tid":1126071,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AfwgQ3S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAfwgQ3S.png&h=e97da146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35aa13344d483f790bda060c4d9ed9e9431a9001","tid":1126071,"uid":64601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"羊界mk"},{"pid":"709f83e2c608f393862e420193292f8613d8844d","tid":1126071,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6416adf9faca5f420646a559b6bf5cac905a8e60","tid":1126071,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s85.youtaker.com/other/2018/10-11/oth676296265c3aeea140bd64f7896268e9769ea0df6854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs85.youtaker.com%2Fother%2F2018%2F10-11%2Foth676296265c3aeea140bd64f7896268e9769ea0df6854.jpg&h=87c31fdf&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}